text: Nick Careen is a Newfoundland and Labrador politician. He was elected to Newfoundland and Labrador's provincial House of Assembly in the 1993 Newfoundland general election as a Progressive Conservative. He represented Placentia District from 1993 to 1996. Careen also unsuccessfully ran as an Independent candidate in the February 2006 by-election in Placentia—St. Mary’s. He placed second winning 1,641 votes. In January 2007, he was appointed to the board of directors of Marine Atlantic.Transport Canada - News Release No. H 005/07, January 26, 2007 - Appointment to Marine Atlantic Inc. ==Election results (partial)== ==References== Category:Progressive Conservative Party of Newfoundland and Labrador MHAs Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Placentia, Newfoundland and Labrador
